  "detailed_description": "Big Fish Editor's Choice!<br />\r\nThis title was chosen for its high standard of quality and amazingly positive reviews.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe bestselling Dark Parable series continues with The Little Mermaid and the Purple Tide! Follow the clues as they take you to an underwater kingdom in this exciting hidden-object puzzle adventure game!  You've been called to investigate a strange purple tide. And that's when the mermaid shows up...<br />\r\n<br />\r\n-\tA variety of hidden-object scenes, including fractured objects!<br />\r\n-\tThe bonus game unlocks the secrets of Prasino's mad king<br />\r\n-\tAchievements <br />\r\n-\tAvailable Strategy Guide <br />\r\n-\tWallpapers and concept art",
